title: rybako
author: rybako
content: Today, I learned that the longest place name in the world has 85 letters and is located in New Zealand. It is "Taumatawhakatangihangakoauauotamateaturipukakapikimaungahoronukupokaiwhenuakita natahu", which means "the place where Tamatea, the man with the big knees, who slid, climbed and swallowed mountains, known as 'landeater,â€™ played his flute to his loved one."https://www.boredpanda.com/interesting-life-facts/How about you?
